name: Marinadelookup
0:
”Alexa, open marinade lookup”
”I want to cook mexican beef”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: marinade lookup
des:
Ask Marinade lookup if you want to cook a certain style or cuisine with a type of meat but unsure what flavors to use.
e.g. I want to cook asian chicken. Pick from Asian, european, mexican and indian with your chosen meat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
